# Archived Pine Scripts

This folder contains deprecated TradingView Pine Script versions.

## Archive Policy
- Older versions replaced by newer updates
- Scripts no longer in use

## Archive Contents
- Original Pine Script code
- Date archived
- Reason for archiving
- Current version

## Format
Each archived script should be saved as:
`archived/pine_scripts/[script_name]_v[X.X.X]_archived_[YYYY-MM-DD].pine`

